    "Id": "177406",
    "ThreadId": "52671",
    "Html": "Hi Bharti,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nIt doesn't look like we expose the Checked and Unchecked events on DataGridCheckBoxColumn, so I would recommend trying a DataGridTemplateColumn with a CheckBox in the CellTemplate, like so:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#a31515;font-size:13px\">DataGrid</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\"> &lt;</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#a31515;font-size:13px\">DataGrid.Columns</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">   &lt;</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#a31515;font-size:13px\">DataGridTemplateColumn</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">     &lt;</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#a31515;font-size:13px\">DataGridTemplateColumn.CellTemplate</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">       &lt;</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#a31515;font-size:13px\">DataTemplate</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">         &lt;</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#a31515;font-size:13px\">CheckBox</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#ff0000;font-size:13px\"> Checked</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">=&quot;CheckBox_Checked&quot;/&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">        &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#a31515;font-size:13px\">DataTemplate</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">     &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#a31515;font-size:13px\">DataGridTemplateColumn.CellTemplate</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">   &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#a31515;font-size:13px\">DataGridTemplateColumn</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">  &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#a31515;font-size:13px\">DataGrid.Columns</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#a31515;font-size:13px\">DataGrid</span><span style=\"font-family:courier new;color:#0000ff;font-size:13px\">&gt;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
