    "Html": "<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">Hi Samanth<br>\r\nI did as suggested as below:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&lt;toolkit:DataGrid.Columns&gt;<span style=\"\">                    </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                    </span>&lt;toolkit:DataGridTextColumn<span style=\"\">     </span>Binding=&quot;{Binding Path=TimeOfValidity,<span style=\"\">  </span>Mode=OneWay}&quot; IsReadOnly=&quot;True&quot;<span style=\"\">  </span>Width=&quot;170&quot;/&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">               </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\"> </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\"> </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                    </span>&lt;toolkit:DataGridTemplateColumn &gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                        </span>&lt;toolkit:DataGridTemplateColumn.CellTemplate&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                            </span>&lt;DataTemplate&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                                </span>&lt;CheckBox Checked=&quot;CheckBox_Checked&quot; Unchecked=&quot;CheckBox_Checked&quot;/&gt;<span style=\"\">                                </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                            </span>&lt;/DataTemplate&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                        </span>&lt;/toolkit:DataGridTemplateColumn.CellTemplate&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">         </span><span style=\"\">           </span>&lt;/toolkit:DataGridTemplateColumn&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\"> </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\"> </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                    </span>&lt;toolkit:DataGridTextColumn<span style=\"\">     </span>Binding=&quot;{Binding Path=Range,<span style=\"\">           </span>Mode=OneWay}&quot; IsReadOnly=&quot;True&quot;<span style=\"\">  </span>Width=&quot;50&quot;/&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\"> </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">By doing this it fired on both check and uncheck, but then how do I bind this to<span style=\"\">      </span>Binding=&quot;{Binding Path=Used}&quot;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\">I need this because I get my initial values in th egrid from database. </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\"> </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\"> </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\"> </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">My actual code at the moment looks like:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\"> </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">&lt;/toolkit:DataGrid.Resources&gt;<span style=\"\">                </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\"> </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                    </span>&lt;toolkit:DataGridTextColumn<span style=\"\">     </span>Binding=&quot;{Binding Path=TimeOfValidity,<span style=\"\">  </span>Mode=OneWay}&quot; IsReadOnly=&quot;True&quot;<span style=\"\">  </span>Width=&quot;170&quot;/&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">                </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                    </span>&lt;toolkit:DataGridCheckBoxColumn Binding=&quot;{Binding Path=Used}&quot;<span style=\"\">                                            </span>Width=&quot;SizeToHeader&quot;&gt;<span style=\"\">                                          </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                            </span><span style=\"\">                    </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                    </span>&lt;/toolkit:DataGridCheckBoxColumn&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"\">                    </span>&lt;toolkit:DataGridTextColumn<span style=\"\">     </span>Binding=&quot;{Binding Path=Range,<span style=\"\">           </span>Mode=OneWay}&quot; IsReadOnly=&quot;True&quot;<span style=\"\">  </span>Width=&quot;50&quot;/&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\"> </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">Thanks and Regards</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">Bharti</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;o:p&gt;<span style=\"font-family:consolas\"> </span>&lt;/o:p&gt;</p>\r\n",
