    "Html": "Hi Bharti,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nI think you want to bind the IsChecked property of your CheckBox to the Used field, like this:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:consolas\">&lt;toolkit:DataGrid.Columns&gt;                    </span>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    &lt;toolkit:DataGridTextColumn     Binding=&quot;{Binding Path=TimeOfValidity, Mode=OneWay}&quot; IsReadOnly=&quot;True&quot;  Width=&quot;170&quot;/&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">               </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    &lt;toolkit:DataGridTemplateColumn &gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">        &lt;toolkit:DataGridTemplateColumn.CellTemplate&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    </span></span></span>&lt;DataTemplate&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    </span></span></span></span>&lt;CheckBox Checked=&quot;CheckBox_Checked&quot; Unchecked=&quot;CheckBox_Checked&quot; <br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    </span><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">  </span></span></span></span></span></span>IsChecked=&quot;{Binding Path=Used}&quot;/&gt;                                </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    </span></span></span>&lt;/DataTemplate&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    <span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    </span></span>&lt;/toolkit:DataGridTemplateColumn.CellTemplate&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    </span>&lt;/toolkit:DataGridTemplateColumn&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\"><span style=\"font-family:consolas\">    </span>&lt;toolkit:DataGridTextColumn Binding=&quot;{Binding Path=Range, Mode=OneWay}&quot; IsReadOnly=&quot;True&quot;  Width=&quot;50&quot;/&gt;</span></p>\r\n",
